m/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lambrini-Girls-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lambrini-Girls-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lambrini-Girls-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lambrini-Girls-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>还有数十名艺术家加入了抵制今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/the-great-escape">大逃亡音乐</a>节的行列，其中超过一半的艺术家要求音乐节放弃对巴克莱银行的赞助，以声援巴勒斯坦。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-10-best-new-artists-the-great-escape-2023-radar-3443679">我们在 2023 年大逃亡中看到的 10 个最佳新表演</a></strong></li></ul><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_title tdi_77 tdb-single-title td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2" data-td-block-uid="tdi_77"></div><p>这个位于布莱顿的节日是由该银行赞助的，由于该银行对向以色列供应武器的公司进行了金融投资，该银行在加沙当前的事件中引起了争议。</p><p>这个问题首先由发起人 How to Catch a Pig 和 The Menstrual Cramps 乐队发起的请愿书引起关注，此后得到了包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lip-critic">Lip Critic</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">Mary in the Junkyard</a>在内的艺术家的签名。敦促电影节放弃巴克莱银行作为赞助商。</p><p>然后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">由于音乐节与巴克莱银行的联系，Cherym 退出了 Great Escape 演出，</a>之后唱片公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">Alcopop 和 Big Scary Monsters 也</a>加入了抵制并退出了音乐节。</p><p>现在，又有数十人加入抵制这一有争议的合作伙伴关系的行列。最新退出表演的包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、ZHEANI、Rett Madison、Mui Zyu、Hongza、Sarah Crean、LVRA、Ideal Living、Van Zon、COMRAD、Other Half、Cherym 和 Borough Council。</p><p>在谈到不参加音乐节的决定时，兰布里尼女孩发表声明称：“我们今年不会参加大逃亡音乐节。考虑到巴克莱的赞助，这是一种有针对性的文化抵制方式。</p><p> “巴克莱银行向向以色列国防军提供军事技术和武器的公司提供超过 10 亿英镑的金融服务，从而使加沙地带的恐怖现象长期存在。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C53q5Got_UA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C54