068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a>分享了他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968">新单曲“Starburster</a> ”，并宣布了他们第四张专辑“ROMANCE”的详细信息。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968"><strong>Fontaines DC 大胆的复出单曲“Starburster”是他们迄今为止最具实验性的作品</strong></a></li></ul><p>过去一周，这支爱尔兰五人组合一直在预告 2022 年广受好评的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-skinty-fia-album-review-3208706">Skinty Fia</a> 》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-share-teaser-of-new-music-3617208">后续作品</a>，现在宣布他们已与 XL Recordings（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RADIOHEAD">Radiohead</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-krule">King Krule</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-XX">The xx</a> ）签约，制作第四张专辑《ROMANCE》 – 由 James Ford（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ARCTIC-MONKEYS">Arctic Monkeys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/FOALS">Foaals</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/depeche-mode">Depeche Mode</a> ）制作，将于今年 8 月上映。</p><p>该唱片以《Starburster》推出，这首歌的灵感来自主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/GRIAN-CHATTEN">Grian Chatten</a>遭受惊恐发作，并配有由 Aube Perrie（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hives">The Hives</a> ）执导的险恶电影视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Fontaines D.C. - Starburster（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KHocVRUlvkk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968"><em>NME</em>在回顾这首歌曲时指出，</a>它似乎标志着乐队如何“完成了完美的左转”，并补充道：“依靠<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a> Trip-hop 黑色氛围首次在《Skinty Fia》的主打歌中暗示，” 《Starburster》是一首沉思的艺术摇滚野兽，融合了电子音乐和嘻哈元素，更类似于他们的同胞引人注目的同胞（和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-and-fontaines-d-c-s-grian-chatten-team-up-for-the-infectious-better-way-to-live-3542385">最近的合作者</a>） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/KNEECAP">KNEECAP</a> ，Chatten 吐槽道：“<em>如果这是暂时的幸福，我会打你的生意<strong>*BREEEAAAATHE*</strong></em> ”。</p><p> “虚张声势与迷幻结合，主唱说他“<em>比出现的挑战者更难</em>”和“<em>中国日历上的猪</em>”。这段视频也是——关于血液、动物和一群不合群的人试图找到出路的狂热梦想——进一步支持了他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sega-bodega">Sega Bodega</a>作为关键灵感的参考。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968">请在此处阅读完整评论</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3618981" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3618981" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3618981" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle.jpg" alt="方丹特区，2024 年。图片来源：Theo Cottle" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FONTAINES_DC_09_050-Credit-Theo-Cottle-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3618981" class="wp-caption-text">方丹特区，2024 年。图片来源：Theo Cottle</figcaption></figure><p>谈到专辑的标题，贝斯手康纳迪根说：“我们一直有这种理想主义和浪漫的感觉。每张专辑都像《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/fontaines-dc-dogrel-album-review-2474751">Dogrel</a> 》一样直接从爱尔兰的角度观察这一点。第二张专辑（《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-dc-a-heros-death-album-review-2706845">英雄之死</a>》）是关于这种超脱，第三张专辑（《Skinty Fia》）是关于散居国外的爱尔兰性。现在我们看看哪里还有什么可以浪漫的地方。”</p><p>他补充道：“这张唱片是关于决定什么是幻想——有形的世界，或者你脑海中的地方。什么更能代表现实？这对我们来说几乎是一种精神上的感觉。” </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="75" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/fontaines-dc-cover-interview-2022-skinty-fia-3209146">封面上的方丹斯·DC：“人们向我寻求答案。我他妈知道什么？”</a><br /></b></li></ul><p>与此同时，查滕补充说，这张专辑激发了他对“在世界尽头坠入爱河”的“迷恋”。</p><p> “这张专辑是为了保护那小小的火焰，”他说。 “世界末日越大，它就越珍贵。”</p><p> Chatten 摒弃了任何“复古美学”，补充道，《ROMANCE》让乐队“说出了我们长期以来一直想说的话。我从来没有觉得一切都结束了，但感觉轻松了真是太好了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3619064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK.jpg" alt="方丹 D.C. – 《浪漫》" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fontaines_DC_Romance_ARTWORK-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3619064" class="wp-caption-text">方丹斯 DC – 《浪漫》</figcaption></figure><p> Fontaines DC 于 8 月 23 日通过 XL Recordings 发行“ROMANCE”。<a href="https://fontainesdc.x-l.co/romance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订并查看以下曲目列表：</p><p> <strong>1.“浪漫”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“星爆”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“事情就是这样”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“欲望”</strong><br /> <strong>5.《在现代世界》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“虫子”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《摩托车男孩》</strong><br /> <strong>8.《日落》</strong><br /> <strong>9.“马性就是本质”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《死亡纠结》</strong><br /> <strong>11.“最爱”</strong></p><p> 《Romance》将标志着 Fontaines DC 自 2022 年第三张专辑《Skinty Fia》以来的第一首原创音乐。从那时起，他们还翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-fontaines-dc-cover-nick-drakes-cello-song-3407050">尼克·德雷克（Nick Drake）的“大提琴歌曲”，制作了一张合辑</a>。</p><p> 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-massive-attack-and-young-fathers-announce-gaza-benefit-single-3562138">乐队与 Massive Attack 和 Young Fathers 合作，宣布发行限量版 12 英寸单曲，</a>以支持无国界医生组织在加沙的救援工作。EP EP《停火》将于 6 月 1 日发行。</p><p>乐队将在整个夏季进行欧洲巡演，参加音乐节演出，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">六月在格拉斯顿伯里周五的公园舞台上亮相</a>，以及八月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-fontaines-d-c-renee-rapp-pendulum-among-50-new-names-added-to-line-up-3580742">重返雷丁和利兹的主舞台</a>。英国和美国的主要日期将很快公布。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-share-pummelling-new-single-starburster-and-announce-new-album-romance-3619061">Fontaines DC 的帖子分享了新单曲“Starburster”并宣布新专辑“ROMANCE”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 宣布推出新的《折磨诗人》音乐视频，调侃时间，分享新歌词：“连雕像都会崩溃” https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-tortured-poets-music-video-teases-time-shares-new-lyrics-even-statues-crumble-3619048?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=泰勒-斯威夫特-宣布-新-折磨-诗人-音乐-视频-戏弄-时间-共享-新-歌词-甚至-雕像-崩溃Liberty DunworthWed, 17 Apr 2024 15:56:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3619048 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>备受期待的专辑将于周五（4 月 19 日）发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-tortured-poets-music-video-teases-time-shares-new-lyrics-even-statues-crumble-3619048">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 宣布新的“折磨诗人”音乐视频，调侃时间，分享新歌词：“甚至雕像崩溃”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>分享了一段<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>的新视频，并透露了专辑中的一首歌词。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-new-jersey-setlist-photos-3448996">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 新泽西演唱会：每个时代的精彩庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位流行偶像将于本周晚些时候（4 月 19 日星期五）发行她的第 11 张录音室唱片，这是 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">《Midnights》</a>的后续作品。</p><p>现在，在专辑发行前夕，这位歌手在 Instagram 上发布了一段动画短片，充满了关于发行的复活节彩蛋。</p><p>视频于昨晚（4 月 16 日）分享，从指向两点钟的时钟开始。这标志着斯威夫特分享的最新线索，其中包含对那个时代的致敬。此前，该时间出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swifts-self-directed-video-for-karma-featuring-ice-spice-3448830">“Karma (Remix)”音乐视频</a>中，在她分享的一张咖啡艺术图片中，与洛杉矶 Spotify 展览上出现的时钟相同。</p><p>从那里，摄像机离开动画房间，在地板上显示皱巴巴的纸，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swifts-new-music-video-for-lavender-haze-3387935">“薰衣草薄雾”</a>的乙烯基变体，然后进入白色走廊，面对一扇写着“受折磨的诗人”名字的门部门&#39;。然后它会跳出钥匙孔，放大显示 4 月 19 日打开的日历，上面写着“折磨诗人部门发行日”。</p><p>视频的其他细节包括日历上写着“东部时间晚上 8 点音乐视频发布！！”，总计为 14，也是对 4 月 20 日的致敬，这一天也恰好是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">唱片店日</a>。</p><p>更多隐藏的细节包括斯威夫特在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“Eras Tour”</a>钢琴上的照片，大约在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-final-variant-3595989">宣布带有 3 首额外歌曲的 2 个变体的</a>同时，以及她与密友兼合作者<a href="/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>的照片，她最初于 2022 年 10 月在网上发布了这些照片。</p><p>看看下面的剪辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C513vGiuWoo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564